main(_) ->
    Products = [#{"name" => "Laptop", "price" => 1500}, #{"name" => "Smartphone", "price" => 900}, #{"name" => "Tablet", "price" => 600}, #{"name" => "Monitor", "price" => 300}, #{"name" => "Keyboard", "price" => 100}, #{"name" => "Mouse", "price" => 50}, #{"name" => "Headphones", "price" => 200}],

end, Expensive).
